    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2003-07-14</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2003-09-09T19:27:30Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Child Tax Fairness Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) provide a uniform definition of the term &quot;child&quot;; (2) repeal the head of household filing status and establish an exemption of $3,700 for single taxpayers with either a qualifying child, relative, or parent in the household; and (3) exempt means-tested government benefits when determining whether or not over half the cost of a dependent's care is provided by a taxpayer.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
